INSERT INTO `question`(`section`, `question_content`, `a`, `b`, `c`, `d`, `ans`, `sub_section`, `level`, `solution`, `date_posted`) VALUES ('Maths_finished files','A unit vector a makes an angle \\(\\frac{\\pi }{4}\\) with z-axis. If \\({\\bf{a}}+ {\\bf{i}} + {\\bf{j}}\\) is a unit vector, then a is equal to ','\(a\)\\(\\frac{{\\bf{i}}}{2} + \\frac{{\\bf{j}}}{2} + \\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2}}\\)','\(b\)\\(\\frac{{\\bf{i}}}{2} + \\frac{{\\bf{j}}}{2} - \\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}\\)','\(c\)\\( - \\frac{{\\bf{i}}}{2} - \\frac{{\\bf{j}}}{2} + \\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2}}\\)','\(d\)None of these','3','VECTOR ALGEBRA','2','Answer = \(c\)Let \\({\\bf{a}} = l{\\bf{i}} + m{\\bf{j}} + n{\\bf{k}},\\) where \\({l^2} +{m^2} + {n^2} = 1.\\)a makes an angle \\(\\frac{\\pi }{4}\\) with \\(z - \\)axis.\\(\\therefore \\,\\,n = \\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }},\\) \\({l^2} + {m^2} = \\frac{1}{2}\\)     \\(\\ldots{} \\)..(i)\\(\\therefore \\,\\,{\\bf{a}} = l\\,{\\bf{i}} + m\\,{\\bf{j}} + \\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2}}\\)\\({\\bf{a}} + {\\bf{i}} + {\\bf{j}} = (l + 1){\\bf{i}} + (m + 1){\\bf{j}} +\\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}\\)Its magnitude is 1, hence \\({(l + 1)^2} + {(m + 1)^2} = \\frac{1}{2}\\)  .....(ii)From (i) and (ii), \\(2lm = \\frac{1}{2} \\Rightarrow l = m =  - \\frac{1}{2}\\)Hence \\({\\bf{a}} =  - \\frac{{\\bf{i}}}{2} - \\frac{{\\bf{j}}}{2} +\\frac{{\\bf{k}}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}\\).',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
